<div class="container-fluid home-page ">
  <div class="dark-overlay">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col s12">
        <span class="flow-text">
          <h3>Welcome To The Place To Share Your Own Book Story</h3>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="col s8 offset-s2">
        <span class="flow-text">
          <p>Welcome to storybook, Post story from the best and worst in realife and choose for them to be read for world or
            completely private as your own personal daily</p>
        </span>
      </div>
      {{#if user}}
      <div class="col s12">
        <p class="wel-user">{{user.firstName}}, Below is your dashboard</p>
        <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn" href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>

      </div>

      {{else}}
      <div class="col s12">
        <a href="/auth/google" class="btn red darken-1 home-google">
          <i class="fa fa-google left"></i> Login With Google</a>
      </div>

      {{/if }}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="card-panel hoverable center-align">
    <h3>You can Share, Read and Engage with amazing Book Story</h3>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="col s12 center-align">

        <p>StoryBook is a place for people sharing their story like best or worst in their life by posting in our platform.
          <br> Let's enhance your story and other's story with us.
          <br> You can share your story with the world by posting as public or private for your own business.
        </p>
        <div class="col s12 center-align" style="margin-top:10px">
          {{#if user}}
          {{else}}
          <div class="col s12">
            <a href="/auth/google" class="btn red darken-1 home-google">
              <i class="fa fa-google left"></i> Login With Google</a>
          </div>

          {{/if }}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container main-section1 center-align">
      <div class="col s12">
        <img src="./img/index-home/begin-state.jpeg" alt="" class="responsive-img">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row center-align">

    <div class="col s4">
      <a href="#" class="fa fa-archive fa-promo"></a>
      <h3>Archievment</h3>
      <p>Our platform tends to assist all users to share their journal daily or planning to make a book to establish by themselve
        in order to promote their book.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col s4">
      <a href="#" class="fa fa-book fa-promo"></a>
      <h3>Safety</h3>
      <p>Our platform provides some options for them to upload their journal like
        <strong>private</strong> or
        <strong>public</strong> in order to ensure their copyright.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col s4">
      <a href="#" class="fa fa-user fa-promo"></a>
      <h3>Keep In Touch</h3>
